1. Download tomocat: 
    $ wget https://dlcdn.apache.org/tomcat/tomcat-8/v8.5.84/bin/apache-tomcat-8.5.84.tar.gz

2. unzip tar file
    $ tar -xvf apache-tomcat-8.5.84.tar.gz
    
3. Goto Directory
    $ cd apache-tomcat-8.5.84
    $ cd bin
    
    Run 
    $ ./startup.sh ............. To start tomcat server
